                <h3>Reproductive Years</h3>
                <p><strong>Focus areas:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                  <li>Family planning or contraception</li>
                  <li>Preconception health if planning pregnancy</li>
                  <li>Regular screenings (Pap tests, breast exams)</li>
                  <li>STI prevention and testing</li>
                  <li>Management of reproductive concerns (PCOS, endometriosis, fibroids)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
